WEBVTT

00:02:01.763 --> 00:02:03.697
Na kabla ya kutoka kwenye chumba,

00:02:03.721 --> 00:02:06.657
tunawaambia wasichungulie kwenye kadi.

00:02:07.518 --> 00:02:08.934
Bila shaka,

00:02:08.958 --> 00:02:11.119
tuna kamera zilizofichwa katika chumba

00:02:11.143 --> 00:02:12.938
kuangalia kila hatua yao.

00:02:14.216 --> 00:02:17.633
Kwasababu haja ya kushinda
mchezo ni kubwa sana,

00:02:17.657 --> 00:02:21.143
zaidi ya asilimia 90 ya watoto 
watachungulia

00:02:21.167 --> 00:02:22.604
mara tutakapotoka chumbani.

00:02:22.628 --> 00:02:24.628
(Kicheko)

00:02:25.044 --> 00:02:27.030
Swali la msingi ni:

00:02:27.054 --> 00:02:29.802
Tutakaporudi na kuuliza watoto

00:02:29.826 --> 00:02:32.135
Kama wamechungulia au la,